news.title: Cu Chi Tunnels Luxury Tour - Morning or Afternoon
news.content: Hear stories of the American-Vietnam war as you discover the maze-like Cu Chi Tunnels, a 136-mile (220 kilometers) network of underground tunnels used by the Viet Cong soldiers. Step back in time as you peek into the old storage areas, poke your head through camouflaged trapdoors, and crawl through military supply tunnels.Read more about Cu Chi Tunnels Luxury Tour - Morning or Afternoon - https://www.viator.com/tours/Ho-Chi-Minh-City/Cu-Chi-Tunnels-halfday-small-group/d352-20086P1?mcid=56757
news.author: Tan Phuoc

news.title: Ha Long Bay Cruise Day Tour - Cave, Kayaking, Swimming & Lunch
news.content: Escape Hanoi and discover Ha Long Bay, the Ha Long Warf, Sung Sot Cave, and the tranquil Ti Top Island. Kayak at Luon Cave, and swim in the blue waters of the crescent-shaped Titov beach. Feel the warm sunshine and the cool breeze while cruising along Ha Long Bay Explore the shimmering stalactites embodying unique shapes of the Sung Sot cave Uncover the stunning beauty of the Luon Cave while kayaking on the blue water Enjoy a sunset party on the boat with red wine, cake, fruits, and more Spend some time in the water or trek to the Titop peak for panoramic views Read more about Ha Long Bay Cruise Day Tour - Cave, Kayaking, Swimming & Lunch - https://www.viator.com/tours/Hanoi/Ha-Long-Bay-Bai-Tu-Long-2-days-cruise/d351-102255P1?mcid=56757
news.author: Tan Phuong

news.title: Morning Small group to Marble Mountains - Am Phu Cave - Monkey Mountain
news.content: Explore the Marble Mountains from Hoi An on this small-group guided morning tour that includes transport. Visit Am Phu Cave, Monkey Mountain, and the largest Lady Buddha statue in Vietnam, with an English speaking guide to provide insightful commentary. Includes round-trip transfers, lunch, and entrance fees to Marble Mountains.Read more about Morning Small group to Marble Mountains - Am Phu Cave - Monkey Mountain - https://www.viator.com/tours/Da-Nang/Morning-Small-group-to-Marble-Mountains-Am-Phu-Cave-Monkey-Mountain/d4680-104142P3?mcid=56757
